# ziti_posture_check_multi_process (Data Source)

A datasource to define a service of Ziti

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "ziti_posture_check_multi_process" "test_ziti_posture_multi_process" {
  filter      = "name contains \"test\""
  most_recent = true
}
```
